| FollowerMemory | ~100 | core/memory/follower_memory.py |
| ConversationState | ~150 | core/conversation/state.py |
| UserContext | ~80 | core/context/user_context.py |

### Priority 2: Services

| Functionality | Lines | New File |
|---------------|-------|----------|
| Intent classification | ~500 | core/intent/classifier.py |
